WEBVTT

01:16.040 --> 01:19.480
I thank all the Sahaja Yogis

01:19.840 --> 01:25.680
from Derbyshire and Birmingham

01:25.920 --> 01:31.120
for giving Me this opportunity to talk to the seekers of this place.

01:38.680 --> 01:40.880
We have seekers in the modern times,

01:41.080 --> 01:43.400
is something very unique.

01:43.600 --> 01:46.680
We never had seekers before,

01:47.040 --> 01:49.760
at least not so many.

01:50.120 --> 01:52.400
There used to be people

01:52.720 --> 01:58.560
who would seek money, as there are many who are seeking these days,

01:59.000 --> 02:05.160
who would seek countries after countries, the power.

02:05.840 --> 02:11.440
There were (not) many who were seeking these

02:12.880 --> 02:20.800
few pearls of bliss of God, very few.

02:22.760 --> 02:25.720
The reason was the awareness,

02:26.080 --> 02:29.480
the collective awareness of human beings

02:30.040 --> 02:33.960
did not think themselves perhaps capable

02:34.480 --> 02:40.880
or perhaps needing some seeking.

02:41.640 --> 02:46.720
But today it's such a beautiful combination

02:47.120 --> 02:52.720
that there are seekers of very high quality born on this earth.

02:53.240 --> 02:56.800
Those who are seeking are in masses.

02:57.040 --> 02:59.480
They are not one or two here and there

02:59.760 --> 03:02.480
sitting on top of a mountain,

03:02.760 --> 03:07.240
cave or something and trying to meditate,

03:07.440 --> 03:10.640
but there are so many who are seeking,

03:11.000 --> 03:17.040
who feel dissatisfied with themselves, with whatever they have.

03:17.360 --> 03:21.320
They think there must be something beyond.

03:21.800 --> 03:28.440
Those who feel that they have not yet found their meaning,

03:28.640 --> 03:33.200
those who feel they have to find the purpose of their life,

03:33.520 --> 03:35.280
those who feel

03:35.480 --> 03:37.960
that there has to be something higher

03:38.160 --> 03:41.680
than what they are into,

03:41.880 --> 03:49.840
all such people are seekers, not of today but of thousands of years.

03:53.400 --> 03:57.360
At the time of Christ there were none, I should say,

03:57.560 --> 04:02.640
because even the ones Christ took as His disciples,

04:02.840 --> 04:04.840
they were actually forced into it;

04:05.080 --> 04:07.840
and He had to go and seek them and find them out

04:08.080 --> 04:10.960
and tell them about it.

04:12.520 --> 04:18.360
So we have to say that these are very important times

04:18.560 --> 04:20.720
in the history of creation,

04:20.920 --> 04:23.200
where there are so many seekers.

04:23.400 --> 04:26.080
But the problem with the seekers today is this

04:26.320 --> 04:28.920
that they don't know what they are seeking.

04:29.160 --> 04:32.240
They have no idea as to what to seek,

04:32.520 --> 04:36.600
how to seek, what to expect.

04:36.880 --> 04:39.320
It's an unknown area they are entering into.

04:39.520 --> 04:42.040
It's very unknown to them.

04:42.840 --> 04:46.760
And this unknown area which they are seeking

04:47.320 --> 04:50.600
is now represented by so many people.

04:50.800 --> 04:53.400
Everyone says, "I'm the one who will deliver the goods."

04:53.600 --> 04:56.120
Another one says, "I'm the one who can do it."

04:56.320 --> 05:01.520
Naturally confusion is created,

05:01.760 --> 05:07.400
as it is, modern times are the times of confusion, great confusion.

05:07.680 --> 05:13.000
And when there such a confusion comes in, then only we find out

05:13.760 --> 05:17.200
a great solution also, a permanent solution

05:17.480 --> 05:19.840
to solve the problem once for all.

05:20.040 --> 05:23.520
There has been never such confusion in the minds of human beings

05:23.720 --> 05:28.120
as it is today as to the right or wrong. Never so much.

05:28.320 --> 05:31.880
Whatever was said, "This was not good," they would do,

05:32.360 --> 05:34.400
knowingly that they are doing wrong.

05:34.640 --> 05:36.280
If they were good people, they would say,

05:36.480 --> 05:38.440
"All right, this is good, we'll do the good."

05:38.720 --> 05:44.560
But everybody knew that this was wrong or right. They may do it.

05:44.920 --> 05:49.080
But today no one knows what is wrong and what is right.

05:49.440 --> 05:52.480
Apart from wrong and right, it's much beyond that,

05:52.680 --> 05:54.640
you have to know yourself.

05:54.840 --> 05:58.840
Because this awareness is within us that we do not know ourselves,

05:59.120 --> 06:02.120
we do not know the absolute. We live in a relative world.

06:02.360 --> 06:04.840
Of this everybody seems to be conscious,

06:05.040 --> 06:09.240
maybe in the subconscious or maybe in the unconscious,

06:09.680 --> 06:13.360
but definitely there's a feeling in every one of us

06:13.560 --> 06:15.960
that "We do not know."

06:16.200 --> 06:18.720
And it's a very honest feeling,

06:18.920 --> 06:21.240
it's a very sublime feeling

06:21.440 --> 06:24.000
that we have to know something more.

06:24.240 --> 06:28.680
Now when we say the word "know," we think as if I would say,

06:28.880 --> 06:32.280
"I don't know about Derbyshire, I have never been there."

06:32.600 --> 06:33.880
Now this means what?

06:34.080 --> 06:36.840
I don't know about Derbyshire.

06:37.040 --> 06:38.920
What don't I know about Derbyshire?

06:39.120 --> 06:41.680
I can read it in the books, I can find out.

06:41.880 --> 06:44.560
I can know all the history of Derbyshire.

06:44.760 --> 06:46.960
I can find out who were the people who,

06:47.160 --> 06:49.080
who were making beautiful porcelain here,

06:49.280 --> 06:50.920
I can find out all about their history,

06:51.120 --> 06:52.520
everything I can read about it.

06:52.760 --> 06:56.080
Still, why should I say I don't know anything about Derbyshire?

06:56.360 --> 06:58.880
Because I have not been to Derbyshire before.

06:59.080 --> 07:01.960
I have not been to Derby, I have not been to this area,

07:02.280 --> 07:04.920
I have not seen this place, I have not visited it,

07:05.120 --> 07:09.360
I have had no experience of this place, so I don't know about it.

07:09.560 --> 07:12.280
This is exactly what is the situation.

07:12.480 --> 07:16.280
The situation is that we do not know about the Divine.

07:16.480 --> 07:19.480
We have read about it, we have heard about it.

07:19.720 --> 07:21.440
So many people have written about it.

07:21.640 --> 07:24.080
Once they know there's an enquiry about it,

07:24.280 --> 07:26.600
they come out with books. Books after books,

07:26.800 --> 07:28.880
thousands of books they have written.

07:29.160 --> 07:32.200
How many of them are true and how many of them are untrue?

07:32.480 --> 07:35.360
It is impossible to find out,

07:35.560 --> 07:38.120
because we do not actually know.

07:38.320 --> 07:39.880
Supposing somebody says

07:40.080 --> 07:43.560
that Duke of Bedford was born in Derbyshire.

07:43.880 --> 07:45.880
Alright, how will I know?

07:46.080 --> 07:47.840
I would not know till I meet somebody

07:48.040 --> 07:52.280
who is really belonging to that place, who knows about it.

07:52.560 --> 07:54.920
In the same way, the knowledge that we have

07:55.120 --> 07:58.920
also about Divine is very confusing.

07:59.120 --> 08:03.200
But this is not knowledge, this is never the knowledge.

08:03.400 --> 08:06.440
The idea of knowledge comes to us

08:06.640 --> 08:14.280
as if it is a kind of an answer to our enquiries

08:14.480 --> 08:17.520
which is rational, which we can understand intelligently

08:17.720 --> 08:19.560
through our intelligence.

08:19.760 --> 08:24.760
But now this area is beyond intelligence, beyond rationality,

08:25.040 --> 08:30.560
beyond all that is limited - is the unlimited area.

08:30.760 --> 08:33.840
All such unlimited areas can be only known

08:34.040 --> 08:38.720
by experience of your awareness.

08:38.920 --> 08:42.200
Now this one should understand is a very delicate thing,

08:42.400 --> 08:46.960
how to know something, an experience of our awareness.

08:47.160 --> 08:50.240
Not an experience, they suddenly see a light, so it's an experience.

08:50.480 --> 08:52.200
I mean, you can always see a light!

08:52.560 --> 08:56.920
So great the people feel about it that they have seen some light

08:57.160 --> 08:59.400
suddenly sparking before them. Nothing so great.

08:59.600 --> 09:02.680
There could be some area from there a sparking can come,

09:02.880 --> 09:06.280
and maybe it is of no use to you,

09:06.480 --> 09:08.960
but just you might feel that you have experienced.

09:09.200 --> 09:13.160
So one must know that seeing is not experiencing.

09:13.360 --> 09:17.600
For example, a dog sees this instrument,

09:18.440 --> 09:23.080
but what does he know about it? He sees it.

09:25.760 --> 09:29.080
Awareness, the human awareness

09:29.320 --> 09:32.080
has so many great things about itself,

09:32.280 --> 09:35.960
compared to the animal awareness.

09:36.400 --> 09:41.760
For example, we can say the awareness of beauty - animals don't have,

09:41.960 --> 09:46.880
awareness of cleanliness - animals don't have.

09:47.360 --> 09:51.320
Human beings have these

09:51.720 --> 09:54.480
built within themselves, they can feel it.

09:54.720 --> 09:58.800
They can feel it on their central nervous system.

09:59.000 --> 10:00.920
So whatever is your awareness,

10:01.120 --> 10:03.840
is to be felt on your central nervous system.

10:04.080 --> 10:06.120
It's not just an imaginary thing

10:06.320 --> 10:08.520
or an intellectual discussion,

10:08.720 --> 10:11.320
"Ah, yes, yes, I know, I know" - not that way.

10:11.520 --> 10:17.400
The knowledge should come to you through your feelings,

10:17.960 --> 10:20.640
like I can feel this is hot or cold,

10:20.840 --> 10:24.400
but a stone will not feel anything.

10:24.800 --> 10:26.680
In the same way, the feeling has to come

10:26.920 --> 10:28.360
through your central nervous system.

10:28.560 --> 10:33.480
That means your awareness itself is to be going, has to be charged.

10:33.720 --> 10:35.760
It has to get a new dimension;

10:35.960 --> 10:39.320
your awareness itself has to get a new dimension.

10:39.520 --> 10:40.880
All other experiences

10:41.080 --> 10:44.240
have no meaning whatsoever in evolution, if you see.

10:45.280 --> 10:49.320
In evolutionary process it is the awareness that improves,

10:49.560 --> 10:53.360
receives better and better dimensions.

10:53.680 --> 10:56.240
And these dimensions have reached its maximum

10:56.480 --> 10:58.840
at the time when you become a human being,

10:59.040 --> 11:03.880
where your awareness is just ready to receive

11:04.240 --> 11:09.720
the awareness of the Universal Being, of the Collective Being,

11:09.920 --> 11:12.720
so that you become the collective being.

11:12.960 --> 11:16.080
Now I would like to tell you about this within ourselves,

11:16.280 --> 11:17.760
how we are placed.

11:17.960 --> 11:20.720
For every practical purposes

11:21.000 --> 11:24.400
you should not take Me for granted,

11:24.640 --> 11:27.480
but you should not also deny what I tell you.

11:27.680 --> 11:31.880
It's like entering into a new university:

11:32.160 --> 11:36.840
We listen to the professor and we try to follow him.

11:37.200 --> 11:39.520
Supposing he propounded,

11:39.720 --> 11:44.960
he propounds a hypothesis before you,

11:45.280 --> 11:50.600
then you just start judging it, work it out.

11:50.800 --> 11:58.040
If it is true, then you call it a law.

11:58.360 --> 12:04.680
In the same way, we should enter into this new understanding

12:04.880 --> 12:08.440
by first seeing it, not denying it.

12:08.640 --> 12:12.120
then if it is true, then we have to believe it.

12:12.360 --> 12:15.240
There should be no blind faith about Sahaja Yoga.

12:15.440 --> 12:17.880
Blind faith does not help at all.

12:18.120 --> 12:20.960
Neither there should be a denial.

12:21.240 --> 12:23.320
And with that cheerful attitude

12:23.520 --> 12:26.960
if you just listen to Me as a hypothesis whatever I'm telling you,

12:27.160 --> 12:29.880
you need not accept it as truth just now.

12:30.080 --> 12:34.080
But then the time has come for Me to prove the truth to you!

12:34.280 --> 12:37.360
And the truth can be proved to you.

12:37.560 --> 12:40.640
Time has come to prove the existence of God;

12:40.840 --> 12:45.880
to prove, not prove that I give you a big lecture

12:46.080 --> 12:48.560
or take you to courts or some sort of a thing like that,

12:48.800 --> 12:53.720
but how am I going to prove it? On your awareness.

12:54.160 --> 13:01.480
It is going to be absolute experience of your awareness

13:01.720 --> 13:07.800
that you are going to feel God Almighty!

13:08.080 --> 13:14.640
Time has come to prove the scriptures, all the scriptures.

13:14.880 --> 13:20.840
The time has come to prove your own connection with God,

13:21.040 --> 13:23.320
your own relationship with Him,

13:23.520 --> 13:26.840
your own relationship with that Primordial Being,

13:27.040 --> 13:28.920
whether you call it "God" or anything,

13:29.120 --> 13:31.640
it makes no difference to God Himself.

13:31.840 --> 13:34.800
Whether you call Him by any name, there is God,

13:35.000 --> 13:38.280
and that God is not the way you conceive God,

13:38.480 --> 13:41.920
it's not the way you understand God or you know God,

13:42.200 --> 13:45.240
but is the God as He is.

13:45.480 --> 13:50.880
Unless and until you yourself feel Him,

13:51.120 --> 13:52.960
you are not going to believe in Him.

13:53.200 --> 13:55.880
Even if you believe under certain circumstances,

13:56.080 --> 13:58.040
it's a belief that is blind.

13:58.240 --> 14:01.640
It has no meaning for any intelligent person,

14:01.840 --> 14:03.600
and the day will come that such a person

14:03.800 --> 14:07.200
is going to denounce that kind of a blind faith.

14:07.440 --> 14:09.680
So now within ourselves, as I said,

14:09.880 --> 14:13.680
is a built-in system which has come to us

14:13.880 --> 14:17.920
through our ascent in our awareness at different stages,

14:18.120 --> 14:20.640
which is like a history written within ourselves

14:20.840 --> 14:23.160
how we become human beings.

14:23.400 --> 14:25.880
Into different stages we were divided.

14:26.240 --> 14:29.240
First of all the stage of the carbon,

14:29.480 --> 14:33.480
where we became alive,

14:33.680 --> 14:36.880
the dead became the life.

14:37.080 --> 14:39.240
That is placed at that point.

14:39.440 --> 14:43.080
It is below that great power within us

14:43.280 --> 14:47.600
which lies in the triangular bone, which we call as Kundalini.

14:47.800 --> 14:54.280
This power is the power also described in the Bible

14:54.560 --> 14:56.400
as the 'Tree of Life',

14:56.600 --> 14:58.960
'I'll appear before you like tongues of flames',

14:59.160 --> 15:02.080
but Bible being a very microscopic thing,

15:02.360 --> 15:05.960
it cannot be explained, the symbolism of that,

15:06.200 --> 15:10.040
unless and until you get your new awareness

15:10.240 --> 15:14.160
or the vibratory awareness, it cannot be explained.

15:14.360 --> 15:18.400
Now this power is the power of desire,

15:18.640 --> 15:22.560
of the ultimate desire, the only desire, the real desire

15:22.800 --> 15:24.800
that we have within ourselves.

15:25.040 --> 15:29.720
All other desires become useless.

15:29.920 --> 15:31.960
See in the affluent countries now

15:32.200 --> 15:36.760
people have achieved affluence; they are rich, well-to-do;

15:37.200 --> 15:39.960
but they are not happy.

15:40.280 --> 15:44.720
People who are extremely affluent like in Sweden

15:44.960 --> 15:49.600
and in Switzerland, they're competing among themselves,

15:49.840 --> 15:54.080
how many youths are going to commit suicide!

15:54.280 --> 16:00.120
Recently I learnt that Swiss people are "better off"-

16:00.320 --> 16:03.280
many more Swiss people are committing suicide

16:03.520 --> 16:09.600
than the people who were young people in Sweden.

16:09.800 --> 16:14.520
This is the state where we should realise that affluence,

16:14.720 --> 16:18.560
if it was our desire, is not the real desire;

16:18.760 --> 16:20.840
because when we got the affluence

16:21.040 --> 16:23.680
we should have been very happy and joyous people.

16:23.880 --> 16:25.560
But we are not.

16:25.760 --> 16:28.680
And the basics of economics is that

16:28.880 --> 16:30.960
wants in particular may be satiable,

16:31.240 --> 16:33.840
but in general they are never satiable,

16:34.040 --> 16:38.360
means, matter cannot satisfy your wants.

16:38.560 --> 16:42.600
So what is the want, what is the seeking one has?

16:42.800 --> 16:46.280
Is hidden in this power,

16:46.520 --> 16:50.760
and that is the seeking to become one with God,

16:50.960 --> 16:53.840
the yoga, the union with God,

16:54.120 --> 16:57.160
what we call the baptism.

16:57.440 --> 17:02.240
In the Koran it's called as the pir.

17:02.440 --> 17:05.800
You have to become the pir, the "twice born."

17:06.080 --> 17:08.920
It is described in various languages,

17:09.120 --> 17:11.960
but the same thing that they have described

17:12.160 --> 17:14.640
is the same in every scripture.

17:14.840 --> 17:19.240
If you try to follow what it means,

17:19.440 --> 17:23.800
you'll be amazed that they all said the same things.

17:24.200 --> 17:27.080
Now somebody might say, 'There might be some other methods, Mother,

17:27.280 --> 17:29.160
it can be something else that can work it out.'

17:29.400 --> 17:31.040
There's no other method,

17:31.240 --> 17:35.480
because this has been worked out for thousands and thousands of years

17:35.680 --> 17:38.160
within yourselves since you became carbon.

17:38.360 --> 17:41.720
And it's all arranged within you by nature.

17:42.040 --> 17:46.760
Like somebody can say that a seed has to sprout

17:47.040 --> 17:50.600
by some other method - there is no other method for a seed.

17:50.880 --> 17:54.520
The seed has got a primule and the primule has to be awakened,

17:54.720 --> 17:56.960
is the only way it works out.

17:57.160 --> 18:00.920
In the same way it is going to work out in all of you.

18:01.120 --> 18:04.760
This power is to be shaken within you,

18:04.960 --> 18:07.840
it is to be awakened within you.

18:08.040 --> 18:11.960
If it is awakened within you, it rises.

18:12.320 --> 18:14.360
But what is this power?

18:14.560 --> 18:18.320
This power is to become one with the Spirit.

18:18.520 --> 18:22.120
So this power knows that it has to become

18:22.320 --> 18:27.800
one with the Divine.

18:28.120 --> 18:31.600
Now we have so many other desires,

18:31.800 --> 18:34.480
so we should say, how is it related to that?

18:34.680 --> 18:37.720
It's like this, that we have to say,

18:37.920 --> 18:42.360
'Come to Derbyshire and meet you all, people.'

18:42.560 --> 18:46.560
Now we come all the way, we come up to Guildhall,

18:46.760 --> 18:50.440
come up here, and don't meet you.

18:50.680 --> 18:52.240
Then all My coming,

18:52.440 --> 18:56.720
all My travelling is useless because I've not met you.

18:57.160 --> 18:58.720
It has no meaning whatsoever.

18:58.920 --> 19:01.120
In the same way all other desires

19:01.320 --> 19:07.840
are just to accomplish this desire, the ultimate desire,

19:08.120 --> 19:13.280
the desire to become one with the Divine.

19:13.720 --> 19:16.000
Lots of things can be said about Kundalini.

19:16.200 --> 19:20.480
I must have spoken hundreds of times about Kundalini,

19:20.800 --> 19:23.240
and to know more about it

19:23.440 --> 19:27.440
you will have to get to Sahaja Yoga and know more about it.

19:27.680 --> 19:31.320
But just now I have told you in brief what is this Kundalini,

19:31.560 --> 19:33.760
and how it is placed there.

19:34.120 --> 19:36.880
Now the, above that is the second -

19:37.080 --> 19:40.760
actually the second one we treat as the third one, it looks here -

19:40.960 --> 19:43.600
is the power of,

19:43.800 --> 19:51.480
I would say,  (inaudible) this is the centre of our seeking.

19:52.600 --> 19:55.800
This centre is called as the Nabhi Chakra,

19:56.000 --> 19:58.400
which gives us our seeking.

19:58.600 --> 20:02.960
When we are in the state of animal,

20:03.200 --> 20:08.200
then we seek food through our stomach.

20:08.400 --> 20:10.960
And you will be amazed then when we become human beings

20:11.160 --> 20:16.680
also we seek our money through our stomach.

20:16.880 --> 20:20.280
We may get little diverted here and there,

20:20.480 --> 20:26.840
but ultimately we even seek our God through our stomach.

20:27.080 --> 20:33.960
Surrounding this stomach is the area where one has to cross.

20:34.200 --> 20:40.880
And this area is actually the area of the Masters.

20:41.160 --> 20:45.440
All the Primordial Masters were born in this area,

20:45.680 --> 20:48.560
like Moses, Socrates.

20:48.800 --> 20:52.840
There are main basic ten primordial beings,

20:53.040 --> 20:54.720
who came on this earth,

20:54.920 --> 21:01.760
who came to give us an idea as to our seeking, what we have to do.

21:01.960 --> 21:07.400
Basically they came here to teach us how to balance ourselves,

21:07.640 --> 21:10.200
how to balance, so we can ascend.

21:10.440 --> 21:17.000
Now all these great prophets or primordial beings,

21:17.280 --> 21:20.680
we should say they were the ones who were the masters,

21:21.040 --> 21:25.280
they came to inform us

21:25.480 --> 21:29.240
that if you cross too much onto the left side

21:29.440 --> 21:32.360
or too much on the right side,

21:32.600 --> 21:36.360
then you will be falling in your sustenance,

21:36.560 --> 21:41.360
in your quality as a human being.

21:41.560 --> 21:45.280
As a human being you have to have a sustenance,

21:45.600 --> 21:48.800
and this is the centre that gradually unfolds

21:49.000 --> 21:52.720
the sustenance from animal to higher animals

21:52.920 --> 21:56.760
and to human stage, where a person starts realising

21:56.960 --> 21:59.760
that these sustenance’s exist within us.

21:59.960 --> 22:03.440
That's how all our laws have come.

22:03.640 --> 22:06.040
The Ten Commandments of the Bible

22:06.280 --> 22:08.880
are the ten sustenances that are within us.

22:09.240 --> 22:12.280
These are the ten Gurus who came on this earth

22:12.480 --> 22:18.560
to save human beings from getting out of the middle path,

22:18.760 --> 22:23.800
going more to the left and more to the right.

