41:17.080 --> 41:19.520
he is not going to believe it. He'll say, "This box?

41:19.720 --> 41:22.600
This looks like an ordinary wooden box."

41:22.840 --> 41:26.040
But when you plug in, it shows its power.

41:26.280 --> 41:29.040
In the same way, what you look at human beings

41:29.240 --> 41:36.560
as something very, very ordinary, mundane thing -

41:36.800 --> 41:39.280
for us we take it for granted, ourselves,

41:39.520 --> 41:42.960
we don't know how glorified we are, how great we are,

41:43.160 --> 41:45.960
how God has created us with such difficulty,

41:46.240 --> 41:48.280
with such care, with such love;

41:48.480 --> 41:50.440
for a very special purpose,

41:50.680 --> 41:53.880
that He wants to bestow all His powers upon you.

41:54.080 --> 41:56.960
He wants you to enter into the Kingdom of God

41:57.160 --> 42:02.440
and to enjoy His blessings, His love.

42:02.640 --> 42:05.640
It is something that we cannot believe;

42:05.840 --> 42:08.680
we are so frustrated, we are so disgusted with ourselves,

42:08.880 --> 42:11.080
with our societies, with everything.

42:11.280 --> 42:14.240
But it's not so, it's not so.

42:14.440 --> 42:15.720
It just has to happen.

42:15.920 --> 42:18.840
You are just to be plugged in to the mains and it works,

42:19.040 --> 42:20.800
and it works. It has worked.

42:21.000 --> 42:23.760
It has worked with thousands, and it should work with you.

42:23.960 --> 42:25.760
But the absurd ideas people have,

42:25.960 --> 42:28.920
which is the conception they have that you can pay for it.

42:29.120 --> 42:31.080
I mean, how can you pay for anything that is living?

42:31.280 --> 42:33.400
Have you ever paid anything for that is living?

42:33.600 --> 42:35.840
Like, have you paid anything for getting

42:36.040 --> 42:40.560
a fruit out of a flower? Can you pay to the flower?

42:40.760 --> 42:43.400
"All right, I'll give you one pound, give me a fruit!"

42:43.640 --> 42:45.040
Will it work out?

42:45.240 --> 42:49.120
It's that absurd, that you cannot pay for the living God,

42:49.400 --> 42:51.840
you cannot pay for the living experience

42:52.040 --> 42:55.840
and you cannot pay for the evolutionary process.

42:56.040 --> 43:00.360
It is spontaneous, it is within ourselves, it works out.

43:00.560 --> 43:02.600
But we understand money so much

43:02.800 --> 43:04.520
that we can't understand that is free,

43:04.720 --> 43:06.960
though we have got so many things free.

43:07.200 --> 43:09.320
So many things we have got free,

43:09.560 --> 43:12.920
still we don't understand the importance of free things,

43:13.120 --> 43:16.640
because we think whatever is free cannot be great.

43:16.840 --> 43:21.200
Actually all great things have to be free, otherwise we won't exist,

43:21.440 --> 43:22.960
we won't live.

43:23.160 --> 43:27.840
If we didn't get air to breathe freely, we'll not exist.

43:28.040 --> 43:31.120
If it happens sometimes in the airplane or some place,

43:31.320 --> 43:33.160
you should see, then people realise

43:33.360 --> 43:38.440
the importance of those free things which we take it for granted.

43:38.640 --> 43:40.880
So one has to understand the conception

43:41.080 --> 43:44.720
that we have about God, about achieving Him,

43:45.000 --> 43:49.480
about getting into ourselves, is also faulty.

43:49.680 --> 43:53.080
We think that supposing we stand on our heads, we'll get it.

43:53.320 --> 43:57.080
I mean, standing on our heads if we can get God, then

43:57.280 --> 44:01.280
in all evolutionary process they should have stood on their heads!

44:01.480 --> 44:06.520
Or we think that by running these races we'll get it,

44:06.720 --> 44:10.360
or by eating this kind of food or that kind of food,

44:10.560 --> 44:14.800
or by doing this or that we'll get it - is wrong.

44:15.000 --> 44:18.760
But then you may ask that why all these people in religions said

44:18.960 --> 44:24.560
"Thou shall not commit this, thou shall not do that"?

44:24.800 --> 44:26.960
They said it because these are the things

44:27.200 --> 44:30.040
which are required for our sustenance,

44:30.240 --> 44:33.480
for our balancing as a human being.

44:33.680 --> 44:36.680
We lose our balance if we do not do these things.

44:36.880 --> 44:40.800
We have to have the balance; that's why it was said, "Don't do it."

44:41.040 --> 44:43.320
Human beings have a capacity to go to extremes.

44:43.520 --> 44:47.760
I mean, you tell them something - I have known people,

44:48.080 --> 44:52.040
you just tell them that to cure this particular centre

44:52.240 --> 44:56.080
you have to do this asana or you have to do this kind of a thing.

44:56.280 --> 45:00.480
They will do it hundred times, thousand times in one day.

45:00.680 --> 45:04.480
I mean, I never asked them, I said just once in a while you do it,

45:04.680 --> 45:08.120
or once a week - they'll do it hundred times.

45:08.320 --> 45:10.120
We go to extremes.

45:10.320 --> 45:13.680
And that's why, to strike the balance, these people told us,

45:13.880 --> 45:16.960
"Don't do this, don't do that, don't do that."

45:17.160 --> 45:19.800
But then in our ego we say, "Why not? What's wrong?"

45:20.000 --> 45:22.160
All right, go ahead.

45:22.360 --> 45:24.960
When we tell children, "Don't smoke"

45:25.160 --> 45:27.280
"Why not? All my friends are smoking, I'll smoke."

45:27.480 --> 45:31.200
All right, go ahead - smoke, get cancer,

45:31.400 --> 45:34.160
then you'll have a hole here, breathe through that.

45:34.360 --> 45:37.200
After sometime this will go away, the nose will go away,

45:37.400 --> 45:40.440
and you'll be moving like a machine looking at everyone:

45:40.640 --> 45:43.480
you can't talk, you cannot live like a normal person.

45:43.720 --> 45:48.720
Then you, one realises that, "Oh God, I wish I had not smoked."

45:48.920 --> 45:51.440
But in Sahaja Yoga we don't say, "Don't smoke",

45:51.640 --> 45:53.080
because half of the people will walk off.

45:53.280 --> 45:56.040
We never say "Don't drink," never say anything "don't."

45:56.320 --> 45:58.760
We say, "All right, you are doing it, it's all right."

45:58.960 --> 46:04.000
Let this happen. As soon as this happens you just give up yourself,

46:04.240 --> 46:08.280
because when you have found the highest,

46:08.600 --> 46:12.240
then you don't care for all these small things.

46:12.440 --> 46:15.840
All your habits drop out automatically,

46:16.040 --> 46:17.600
I don't have to force you for that.

46:17.800 --> 46:22.600
You have everything within you, that power, like you get lifted up.

46:22.800 --> 46:27.400
Like a lotus that rises out of the mire by its own force,

46:27.600 --> 46:30.680
you come up and your fragrance fills that mire,

46:30.880 --> 46:32.840
and you are amazed at it yourself.

46:33.040 --> 46:35.840
First you are identified with that mire,

46:36.040 --> 46:39.000
and you think that this is what it is - but it's not so.

46:39.200 --> 46:44.360
When it comes up, that lotus, it spreads its beautiful petals,

46:44.600 --> 46:49.760
and the fragrance gives us that personality which spreads all over.

46:49.960 --> 46:51.960
And that's what is going to happen to you.

46:52.160 --> 46:57.400
All of you are going to be that lotus which looks hidden,

46:57.640 --> 47:03.400
which is absolutely invisible within you,

47:03.600 --> 47:04.920
which is going to open out,

47:05.120 --> 47:09.960
and the fragrance of your divinity is going to spread.

47:10.160 --> 47:12.720
Now today I cannot cover all the centres,

47:12.920 --> 47:14.480
because if I start covering all the centres

47:14.680 --> 47:16.480
it will be a very lengthy thing.

47:16.680 --> 47:19.040
I have covered three centres as you have seen:

47:19.240 --> 47:22.920
the Mooladhara Chakra, the Swadisthana and the Nabhi Chakra,

47:23.120 --> 47:25.600
and others I'll cover later on tomorrow.

47:25.800 --> 47:27.960
But I must talk about the Spirit,

47:28.160 --> 47:34.320
about which we are talking for ages now

47:34.520 --> 47:36.640
that we have to become the Spirit.

47:36.840 --> 47:43.040
Now English language, as you know, "spirit" can be anything.

47:46.360 --> 47:50.080
It's a very ambiguous word:

47:50.280 --> 47:53.360
even to alcohols we call it spirits,

47:53.560 --> 47:55.720
even to the dead souls we call them spirits,

47:55.960 --> 47:58.960
and even to the Spirit that is we are,

47:59.200 --> 48:04.840
the pure being which is called as "atma" in Sanskrit language,

48:05.240 --> 48:06.720
we call the word "spirit."

48:06.920 --> 48:09.840
Here I am saying, talking about that Spirit

48:10.040 --> 48:13.200
which is the pure being within you,

48:13.400 --> 48:15.280
which is a detached being within you,

48:15.480 --> 48:17.600
which is the witness within you,

48:17.800 --> 48:20.400
which sees you all the time, which watches you,

48:20.600 --> 48:24.440
which resides within you as joy and happiness in the heart.

48:24.640 --> 48:27.640
It resides in the heart.

48:28.040 --> 48:32.040
This Spirit is not in our conscious mind,

48:32.240 --> 48:35.120
is not in our central nervous system,

48:35.320 --> 48:37.880
is not under our control.

48:38.080 --> 48:41.520
To give it an analogy, I say that

48:41.720 --> 48:44.800
the left side within us is like the brake

48:45.000 --> 48:49.040
and the right side is like an accelerator in a car.

48:49.240 --> 48:53.520
Now in the car we are learning driving, sitting in the front seat,

48:53.720 --> 48:56.160
and there is the master watching at the back

48:56.360 --> 48:59.480
and seeing the whole play.

48:59.680 --> 49:02.720
Now what you do is to go to the left

49:02.920 --> 49:05.040
- means sometimes you put the brake,

49:05.240 --> 49:06.880
sometimes you put the accelerator,

49:07.080 --> 49:11.760
make mistakes, and then you learn how to drive.

49:11.960 --> 49:16.120
That learning how to drive is the wisdom part of it,

49:16.320 --> 49:18.480
which comes to us through balancing our lives.

49:18.720 --> 49:22.680
Balance is the most important thing to begin with.

49:22.880 --> 49:24.680
But even if you don't have balance -

49:24.880 --> 49:26.960
I have seen in Sahaja Yoga very imbalanced people

49:27.160 --> 49:30.600
get into the balance.

49:30.920 --> 49:33.720
Now this balancing left and right,

49:33.920 --> 49:37.440
or say, of the brake and the accelerator,

49:37.640 --> 49:39.600
gives you a position where you can say

49:39.800 --> 49:42.240
now you have mastered the driving.

49:42.440 --> 49:45.880
But still there is the master sitting at the back.

49:46.200 --> 49:49.280
Then you become the master.

49:49.560 --> 49:52.160
The master is the Spirit within you.

49:52.360 --> 49:58.720
You become the Spirit, and you start watching yourself as a driver.

49:58.920 --> 50:02.280
The whole thing becomes like a play, like a drama;

50:02.480 --> 50:05.080
that you separate yourself and start seeing

50:05.320 --> 50:07.680
everything happening before your eyes,

50:07.880 --> 50:11.320
everything happening just like a drama outside you,

50:11.520 --> 50:13.840
and you are not the part and parcel of it.

50:14.040 --> 50:16.800
So you enter into the area of your axis,

50:17.000 --> 50:20.640
and the periphery loses its impact on you.

50:20.840 --> 50:27.040
You become a person who is silent, blissful, quiet,

50:27.240 --> 50:29.840
and sees the periphery, the movement of the periphery,

50:30.040 --> 50:31.800
but you are not in it.

50:32.000 --> 50:33.560
That's how you become the master,

50:33.760 --> 50:35.560
that's how you become the prophet.

50:35.800 --> 50:38.560
But Sahaja Yoga today has a power

50:38.760 --> 50:42.560
to make the prophets out of the men of God,

50:42.760 --> 50:47.480
and these prophets will have power to make others prophet -

50:47.680 --> 50:51.280
so says William Blake, the great poet of this country.

50:51.480 --> 50:53.880
And that's exactly what Sahaja Yoga is.

50:54.080 --> 50:56.720
He predicted it hundred years back.

50:56.920 --> 51:00.960
And today if you come to Sahaja Yoga, you'll be amazed what you are.

51:01.160 --> 51:05.320
Whatever he has predicted about England

51:05.560 --> 51:10.320
being the Jerusalem of tomorrow, that tomorrow is today.

51:10.640 --> 51:13.760
This country of yours, England

51:13.960 --> 51:16.280
- which is so far, I don't know if people understand

51:16.480 --> 51:19.000
are aware of what this country is,

51:19.200 --> 51:21.680
which is the heart of the universe,

51:21.880 --> 51:25.160
which is the most important part of the universe

51:25.400 --> 51:27.400
- has to become the Jerusalem.

51:27.600 --> 51:31.360
For that, the Englishmen have to come out of their inertia

51:31.560 --> 51:35.720
to see what are their potentials,

51:35.920 --> 51:39.720
to rise up to that point, and that's going to work out.

51:39.920 --> 51:43.880
It's already is working very well in London.

51:44.080 --> 51:46.960
Of course, we can't have too many people

51:47.160 --> 51:52.760
because plastics can be produced in the machines in thousands,

51:52.960 --> 51:55.680
but if you have to have something living it takes time.

51:55.880 --> 52:00.160
But once it takes time, once it comes to its maturity,

52:00.360 --> 52:02.600
I'm sure this great country is going to assume

52:02.800 --> 52:06.680
that status of becoming Jerusalem,

52:06.920 --> 52:09.880
the place of worship

52:10.120 --> 52:13.800
where people have to come to worship.

52:14.000 --> 52:17.320
It's very surprising, things are happening with Sahaja Yoga,

52:17.520 --> 52:19.920
the flower daisy which never had any fragrance,

52:20.120 --> 52:22.840
if you go and see, now is having fragrance.

52:23.040 --> 52:26.400
Most of the English flowers had no fragrance,

52:26.640 --> 52:28.200
they were known by that.

52:28.400 --> 52:32.280
Most of the flowers are now having tremendous fragrance.

52:32.480 --> 52:34.080
You can see for yourself.

52:34.280 --> 52:38.400
All these things are working by nature, are worked out,

52:38.600 --> 52:41.160
they are coming- but what about human beings?

52:41.360 --> 52:45.120
Where are they? What are they doing? Where are they lost?

52:45.360 --> 52:47.520
This is a very sad thing.

52:47.800 --> 52:51.120
I came to London just by chance, I should say,

52:51.320 --> 52:53.680
or maybe that is pre-arranged.

52:53.880 --> 52:58.640
My husband got elected to this job and he had to come.

52:58.840 --> 53:02.240
And this agency of the UN is only placed here.

53:02.480 --> 53:04.840
It's in England. It's nowhere else.

53:05.040 --> 53:07.920
You have only one agency of the UN, that is in England

53:08.120 --> 53:12.720
for which My husband got elected, and so I am here.

53:13.000 --> 53:16.960
Otherwise, I don't think I could have come here like a Guru,

53:17.200 --> 53:23.560
because I don't have any other interest but this.

53:23.760 --> 53:25.600
And I could not have come here otherwise,

53:25.800 --> 53:30.040
because uninvited I would not come to a country,

53:30.280 --> 53:35.560
but I came here as invited person.

53:35.880 --> 53:37.240
It's all working out.

53:37.440 --> 53:39.640
Only you people have to work it out yourself,

53:39.840 --> 53:42.480
and understand not only the dynamism,

53:42.680 --> 53:45.840
the vitality, but the greatest importance is that

53:46.040 --> 53:48.920
at this point you are standing

53:49.120 --> 53:53.640
on the verge of destruction or construction.

53:53.840 --> 53:56.680
And the English people have a special place.

53:56.880 --> 53:59.440
They have to rise up to it,

53:59.640 --> 54:04.040
because they are the cells of the heart.

54:04.240 --> 54:06.080
I'll have this lecture tomorrow again.

54:06.360 --> 54:08.760
I'll hope you'll come and make it comfortable.

54:09.000 --> 54:09.880
Sorry for My throat,

54:10.080 --> 54:12.880
I have been speaking day in and day out, every day.

54:13.080 --> 54:16.000
Thank you very much.

54:18.440 --> 54:23.520
If you have any questions, I would like to answer them.

54:59.120 --> 55:06.120
Can I have (answers) , questions from you and then I’ll answer.

55:29.520 --> 55:32.840
You said You could cure after Self-Realization.

55:33.040 --> 55:40.960
His problem is that his mother is deaf.

55:44.400 --> 55:49.040
Can You fix that hearing problem?

55:50.560 --> 55:55.480
You see this question is such

55:56.240 --> 56:00.960
that it makes you feel that I am a person who have to cure everyone.

56:01.560 --> 56:03.560
You are sadly mistaken.

56:03.760 --> 56:07.880
It's a by-product of awakening of the Kundalini, you get cured.

56:08.240 --> 56:11.320
I'm sorry for that, that you have this understanding

56:11.520 --> 56:13.560
that I'm here to cure all the people.

56:13.760 --> 56:16.200
I should settle down in a hospital.

56:16.520 --> 56:19.840
But main thing is Kundalini has to be awakened

56:20.160 --> 56:21.880
to get you cured. All right?

56:22.160 --> 56:25.880
If your mother was here we could work it out.

56:26.120 --> 56:28.160
But the main thing you must understand,

56:28.360 --> 56:32.280
that God has lot of common sense as we have,

56:32.480 --> 56:36.280
and He is only interested in such lights

56:36.480 --> 56:45.120
as we are, which will work out His work.

56:45.320 --> 56:51.400
Those who are, say, very sick people, extremely sick,

56:51.600 --> 56:54.240
can get cured in a second.

56:54.440 --> 56:57.400
You'll be amazed I'll tell you,

56:57.800 --> 57:03.160
our President of India, he went to America for his treatment

57:03.360 --> 57:09.560
and it failed. And he was going back to India.

57:09.800 --> 57:14.440
And I went to see him as Mrs. So and So.

57:14.680 --> 57:16.880
But the High Commissioner told him that

57:17.160 --> 57:19.360
I'm So and So and he had heard My name in India.

57:19.600 --> 57:22.360
His wife said, "Why don't you cure my husband?"

57:22.640 --> 57:25.680
And he was just on his last ...

57:25.920 --> 57:30.320
they had prepared everything for his last rites in India.

57:30.520 --> 57:35.120
I just put My hand on his back for ten minutes, you won't believe,

57:35.360 --> 57:37.840
he had not slept for days together with pain,

57:38.040 --> 57:40.240
he said, "My pain is relieved, I want to sleep",

57:40.480 --> 57:42.520
and he got up, he was perfectly all right.

57:42.720 --> 57:45.360
He walked down, people had brought stretchers and things.

57:45.560 --> 57:48.320
He just walked down. They couldn't believe their eyes.

57:48.520 --> 57:52.640
But this has happened because

57:52.840 --> 58:00.560
he is going to be used for the work of God.

58:00.800 --> 58:04.280
In our house if you have lights

58:04.480 --> 58:07.600
which are never going to give light, we don't bother about them.

58:07.800 --> 58:10.560
We sell them in the junk.

58:10.800 --> 58:20.160
In the same way, the Divine doesn't cure people, all of them.

58:20.360 --> 58:24.200
It does many thousands

58:24.400 --> 58:27.560
but some of the people who are very sick,

58:27.760 --> 58:30.760
He says, "All right. You go through the second cycle.

58:30.960 --> 58:33.800
All right? Come back purified,

58:34.000 --> 58:37.240
rested and then it works out."

58:37.440 --> 58:42.560
So not necessarily that everybody will be cured, not necessarily.

58:43.080 --> 58:48.480
But so many have got cured and it has worked.

58:48.680 --> 58:53.320
But that's not our main job, is to give cures to people. No.

58:53.520 --> 58:58.080
It is to give realisation to people and as a by-product as you said,

58:58.280 --> 59:03.280
of course if she gets realisation, her deafness will go away.

59:03.600 --> 59:06.240
Many people have cured their deafness.

59:06.440 --> 59:10.040
Not only deafness but even bald headed people have got hair.

59:10.240 --> 59:15.960
He had no hair on his head when he came to Me, but I don't say;

59:16.320 --> 59:19.920
that after realisation and before realisation, so tremendous

59:20.120 --> 59:24.320
that it's better to take photographs before realisation

59:24.520 --> 59:26.240
and see yourself - dump sometimes!

59:26.440 --> 59:28.360
After realisation people,

59:28.560 --> 59:30.560
see, they have got their photographs before realisation,

59:30.800 --> 59:33.680
they have thrown them away.

59:34.480 --> 59:35.920
It is different.

59:36.240 --> 59:40.400
But the main thing is not curing, it's the Self-realization.

59:40.880 --> 59:44.400
That's the main thing! And age has no problem.

59:44.600 --> 59:47.800
Yesterday I think in Birmingham, we gave realisation to somebody

59:48.000 --> 59:51.920
who was a very, very old man. So age has no consideration,

59:52.120 --> 59:54.840
health has no consideration, nothing of the kind.

59:55.040 --> 59:58.920
Everyone can get it and should try to get it.

59:59.280 --> 01:00:02.920
All right? So if you can get her, we'll work it out.

01:00:03.160 --> 01:00:05.840
But I don't promise anything. All right?

01:00:06.040 --> 01:00:08.800
May God bless you.

01:00:09.240 --> 01:00:13.600
Of course, Self-realization I promise! That I promise.

01:00:13.800 --> 01:00:18.440
If you have patience with yourself as I have with you.

01:00:19.320 --> 01:00:21.800
You have to have patience.

01:00:22.000 --> 01:00:24.200
Any other question please?

01:00:33.040 --> 01:00:35.440
He has had chest problems for last four or five years.

01:00:35.640 --> 01:00:36.960
Is there any way You can help him?

01:00:37.160 --> 01:00:38.880
Of course, that can be helped.

01:00:39.080 --> 01:00:42.160
Yes, chest problem like breathing trouble or what?

01:00:42.400 --> 01:00:45.560
Breathing trouble? Is he an Indian?

01:00:45.760 --> 01:00:47.680
Asthma. Are you an Indian?

01:00:47.880 --> 01:00:49.840
Ahh, Indians you know.

01:00:50.120 --> 01:00:53.920
They take so much bath. They still think they are in India.

01:00:54.120 --> 01:00:56.360
Everyday take bath in the morning and then go out.

01:00:56.560 --> 01:01:00.400
Isn't it? That should not be done. This is England.

01:01:00.680 --> 01:01:03.840
We should take bath in the night. We should live like English people.

01:01:04.080 --> 01:01:06.840
They are great bathers. Indians are great bathers, you see,

01:01:07.040 --> 01:01:09.200
they must have bath every day

01:01:09.400 --> 01:01:12.920
whether it is zero degrees or minus twelve degrees.

01:01:13.160 --> 01:01:16.920
They must have bath, you see, it's a habit formation they have got.

01:01:17.120 --> 01:01:19.160
They don't feel all right without a bath

01:01:19.360 --> 01:01:21.680
and that's how they develop, but in any case we'll cure your asthma.

01:01:21.880 --> 01:01:25.200
All right? It's not so difficult.

01:01:25.400 --> 01:01:29.680
But one should not take too much bath in England.

01:01:29.880 --> 01:01:33.680
I would suggest that if you want to take bath, take it in the night

01:01:33.880 --> 01:01:37.720
as the English people do, because it's a very treacherous climate.

01:01:38.040 --> 01:01:41.400
And if you take your bath and get out of your bath,

01:01:41.600 --> 01:01:45.240
you are definite to catch these troubles in the chest.

01:01:45.440 --> 01:01:49.200
Not only that but arthritis and all these things come out of this.

01:01:49.440 --> 01:01:51.720
This is very indiscriminating in this country.

01:01:51.960 --> 01:01:56.560
The climate is such you have to be careful.

01:01:57.280 --> 01:02:02.960
I mean, one should not postpone bathing forever.

01:02:04.200 --> 01:02:05.880
Because, you see, when I say something

01:02:06.080 --> 01:02:09.400
I must give the other extreme also.

01:02:09.640 --> 01:02:11.880
But we are great bathers, no doubt you see.

01:02:12.080 --> 01:02:14.600
Personal cleanliness is too much with Indians, too much.

01:02:14.880 --> 01:02:18.880
But general cleanliness or you can say the collective cleanliness

01:02:19.080 --> 01:02:22.840
is more here, you see. Like mowing the lawn and

01:02:23.080 --> 01:02:25.560
looking after the cleanliness of the roads and all much better.

01:02:25.800 --> 01:02:29.440
I mean, we have to combine these things. It's important.

01:02:29.640 --> 01:02:33.000
That can work out. All right? Asthma is not such a problem.

01:02:33.280 --> 01:02:35.440
What else?

01:02:38.480 --> 01:02:40.880
In what way does it work out?

01:02:41.080 --> 01:02:44.280
We have a centre within us which is the centre of Shri Rama

01:02:44.480 --> 01:02:46.840
on the right hand side, we call it the right heart.

01:02:47.160 --> 01:02:49.080
And, if we can cure that centre of yours,

01:02:49.280 --> 01:02:52.880
you'll be all right. All right?

01:02:54.640 --> 01:02:58.960
We'll work it out. We'll tell you how to do it.

01:03:09.680 --> 01:03:12.160
How many thousands of years

01:03:12.360 --> 01:03:16.960
does the yoga date back from?, she said.

01:03:17.960 --> 01:03:19.720
Which yoga you mean?

01:03:19.920 --> 01:03:24.640
Yoga as being the spontaneous Yoga has been there throughout.

01:03:25.040 --> 01:03:27.720
You see, what is spontaneous is living.

01:03:27.960 --> 01:03:30.520
And the living process has been there throughout.

01:03:30.720 --> 01:03:35.400
So we cannot say when it started.

01:03:35.600 --> 01:03:37.880
We can say when it got separated.

01:03:38.160 --> 01:03:40.880
When God and His Power separated

01:03:41.080 --> 01:03:43.760
and God started watching the whole thing as a witness,

01:03:43.960 --> 01:03:48.040
the God Almighty, and His Power started working it out,

01:03:48.320 --> 01:03:50.800
it created all the universes,

01:03:51.000 --> 01:03:55.360
it created our universe out of which it created now human beings.

01:03:55.560 --> 01:03:59.760
And now, it has to become one again.

01:03:59.960 --> 01:04:04.240
That creation has to know its Creator.

01:04:04.520 --> 01:04:12.080
One, two, three, four - there have been always few people

01:04:12.360 --> 01:04:14.840
getting this connection,

01:04:15.040 --> 01:04:18.200
but today is the time for en masse evolution.

01:04:18.480 --> 01:04:23.200
So, for a growth of life you cannot give any time.

01:04:23.400 --> 01:04:25.680
You can't say when it started,

01:04:25.880 --> 01:04:28.720
how many years back it has been on.

01:04:28.920 --> 01:04:30.960
But today is the blossom time

01:04:31.200 --> 01:04:34.760
when many have to get the blessings of yoga.

01:04:34.960 --> 01:04:37.840
All right? Thank you.

01:04:50.480 --> 01:04:52.200
What is it?

01:04:52.760 --> 01:04:54.320
You spoke about Kundalini.

01:04:54.520 --> 01:04:58.960
For the ordinary person, it's very difficult to awaken.

01:04:59.160 --> 01:05:03.360
Ah, who's told you that? It's not so.

01:05:03.600 --> 01:05:05.200
You see it is these abnormal people

01:05:05.400 --> 01:05:07.800
when they talk about Kundalini they call it abnormal

01:05:08.000 --> 01:05:11.520
because they don't know how to do it. It's the easiest thing to do.

01:05:11.760 --> 01:05:15.240
It's the easiest thing to do if you are an awakened person.

01:05:15.480 --> 01:05:17.840
Even a child can do it.

01:05:18.040 --> 01:05:22.440
It's those people who say that Kundalini is very difficult

01:05:22.640 --> 01:05:26.120
are the people who have no idea of Kundalini at all.

01:05:26.320 --> 01:05:32.120
They are not masters. For a master what is difficult?

01:05:32.360 --> 01:05:35.200
And even an ordinary can become a master,

01:05:35.480 --> 01:05:37.400
then what is difficult?

01:05:37.640 --> 01:05:42.160
These are not masters. These are people absolutely naive,

01:05:42.360 --> 01:05:46.880
money makers, useless people.

01:05:47.160 --> 01:05:50.840
They write books without knowing anything about
Kundalini.

01:05:51.080 --> 01:05:53.120
They are the misguiding people.

01:05:53.320 --> 01:05:55.120
It's the easiest thing to do.

01:05:55.360 --> 01:05:58.520
Just under your hand it will move, you will see it moving up

01:05:58.760 --> 01:06:00.400
and you will see it pulsating on the head.

01:06:00.600 --> 01:06:02.840
It's not at all difficult.

01:06:03.040 --> 01:06:05.880
I told you it's the most vital thing that has to happen

01:06:06.080 --> 01:06:12.440
and all that is vital has to be free and easy - sahaja.

01:06:12.920 --> 01:06:14.920
Why? In India we had Nanaka who said,

01:06:15.120 --> 01:06:19.800
"Sahaja samaadhi laago. Sahaja samaadhi laago."

01:06:20.000 --> 01:06:24.120
Nobody said it is difficult. Kabira never said it. He said,

01:06:24.320 --> 01:06:28.200
"Paacho pachiso pakar bulau ek hi dor bandhahu."

01:06:28.400 --> 01:06:32.840
I'll get twenty-five people together and put them onto one thread.

01:06:33.520 --> 01:06:36.360
Those who had the authority always talked like that.

01:06:36.600 --> 01:06:39.080
Nobody said it is difficult.

01:06:39.360 --> 01:06:44.600
It's only these people who do not know the job,

01:06:45.000 --> 01:06:48.560
who have no authority, talk like that.

01:06:48.800 --> 01:06:51.040
Don't believe them.

01:06:51.240 --> 01:06:53.840
It's the easiest thing to do. You will see yourself.

01:06:54.040 --> 01:06:57.840
But supposing it is easiest, then why should we deny it?

01:06:58.120 --> 01:07:00.800
Supposing I've got the diamond for you free,

01:07:01.000 --> 01:07:05.240
won't you see it, won't you have it?

01:07:06.920 --> 01:07:09.920
Or are we going to feel, "Oh it's very difficult. How can we do?"

01:07:10.120 --> 01:07:13.960
When I am saying it is easy. You don't have to pay for it.

01:07:14.560 --> 01:07:16.960
All right?

01:07:19.960 --> 01:07:22.160
What's it?

01:07:26.640 --> 01:07:31.120
No, that's correct. Sit down, sit down.

01:07:31.320 --> 01:07:34.880
All right, all right. Please sit down. I'll tell you.

01:07:35.200 --> 01:07:38.280
That's the method people tried. It doesn't work out that way.

01:07:38.480 --> 01:07:45.240
Say, your car, is something wrong with your car, all right?

01:07:45.480 --> 01:07:51.320
Now, can you clean it from sitting inside it?

01:07:51.760 --> 01:07:56.200
Can you put it right? You have to get out of it.

01:07:56.520 --> 01:07:59.600
So first the Kundalini rising has to be done.

01:07:59.800 --> 01:08:01.800
You see, people have confused everything.

01:08:02.000 --> 01:08:05.480
Even in Hatha Yoga where there are ashtangas,

01:08:05.680 --> 01:08:12.400
first thing is Ishwar Pranidhana. First is the establishment of God!

01:08:12.840 --> 01:08:15.200
First you have to be connected with God.

01:08:15.400 --> 01:08:17.440
Even in Christianity you have to be baptized first.

01:08:17.640 --> 01:08:19.400
Of course, it's an artificial one, forget it,

01:08:19.600 --> 01:08:21.480
but you have to be baptised.

01:08:21.680 --> 01:08:24.520
Even as a Hindu you have to be christened in a way

01:08:24.720 --> 01:08:28.240
what you call a Yagnopavita, is done at the age of eight years.

01:08:28.440 --> 01:08:33.200
That's what realisation is.

01:08:34.800 --> 01:08:37.840
Or Mohammed Sahib and all these people use Sumta (no thoughts),

01:08:38.040 --> 01:08:39.440
that's the same thing.

01:08:39.640 --> 01:08:41.840
So the first thing is to get your realisation.

01:08:42.040 --> 01:08:44.440
It doesn't mean that you become a master.

01:08:44.640 --> 01:08:45.960
But awakening of the Kundalini

01:08:46.160 --> 01:08:49.280
and then with the growth of the Kundalini you become a master.

01:08:49.480 --> 01:08:53.240
This was the real process but they have put it upside down now.

01:08:53.440 --> 01:08:56.040
How can you cleanse yourself

01:08:56.240 --> 01:08:58.680
unless and until you get out of it?

01:08:58.880 --> 01:09:00.840
Supposing My sari is spoilt,

01:09:01.040 --> 01:09:04.640
I have to take out My sari and clean it. Isn't it?

01:09:06.160 --> 01:09:09.520
And that's why it is difficult.

01:09:09.880 --> 01:09:11.880
That is it. It's a confusion they have created.

01:09:12.080 --> 01:09:15.160
And don't believe in all these stories.

01:09:15.400 --> 01:09:18.560
If you try to suppress your ego, it will sit on your head.

01:09:18.800 --> 01:09:20.160
Never it will run away.

01:09:20.360 --> 01:09:25.640
If you try to suppress your super-ego, it will never help you.

01:09:25.840 --> 01:09:27.720
But here automatically it happens,

01:09:27.920 --> 01:09:29.600
and how it happens I'll tell you tomorrow.

01:09:29.800 --> 01:09:32.200
By awakening these deities within yourself

01:09:32.400 --> 01:09:36.000
these things are sucked in. Kundalini awakens and does it.

01:09:36.280 --> 01:09:38.600
And last of all, if you want Me to confess,

01:09:38.800 --> 01:09:41.720
there is something special about Me that I can do it.

01:09:42.040 --> 01:09:44.640
Must be something.

01:09:47.840 --> 01:09:51.040
If you don't crucify Me, I'll say that much, not more.

01:09:51.240 --> 01:09:52.360
You better find out.

01:09:52.560 --> 01:09:55.880
Otherwise the first thing you will do is to crucify Me.

01:09:56.080 --> 01:10:00.600
I don't want it anymore.

01:10:03.840 --> 01:10:06.160
All right? May God bless you.

01:10:08.520 --> 01:10:10.440
Yes, My child?

01:10:21.040 --> 01:10:25.720
It's not any surgery needed for that.

01:10:26.600 --> 01:10:29.120
In Sahaja Yoga, we have techniques,

01:10:29.320 --> 01:10:34.400
divine techniques by which we open our heart.

01:10:34.960 --> 01:10:38.360
The confusion is on another line also,

01:10:38.560 --> 01:10:41.320
and this confusion has led us into problem.

01:10:41.520 --> 01:10:45.960
You see, the confusion is about how our relationships

01:10:46.200 --> 01:10:51.200
should be to ourselves, to others and to the society.

01:10:51.400 --> 01:10:55.440
There's a big confusion that started long time back.

01:10:55.640 --> 01:10:57.160
When the Smritis were written,

01:10:57.400 --> 01:10:59.320
or we can say when the religion was practiced

01:10:59.520 --> 01:11:02.440
it was just the other way round. We started doing everything

01:11:02.640 --> 01:11:07.920
and that's how we have lost that capacity.

01:11:08.320 --> 01:11:10.960
The attitude towards ourselves should be

01:11:11.160 --> 01:11:13.920
that we should try to perfect ourselves.

01:11:14.120 --> 01:11:17.120
It's absolutely tyrannical I tell you.

01:11:17.320 --> 01:11:21.840
When I tried to perfect Sahaja Yoga, I am tyrannical towards Myself.

01:11:22.200 --> 01:11:24.320
The amount of work I take out of this body

01:11:24.520 --> 01:11:28.640
and the amount of exertions I can put in out of this body,

01:11:28.880 --> 01:11:32.960
the stretching of My complete patience to a great extent

01:11:33.160 --> 01:11:33.920
- I work it out.

01:11:34.120 --> 01:11:36.760
I mean, normally you know, people get just clenched up,

01:11:37.000 --> 01:11:38.640
"Oh Mother, this is too much. We can't bear."

01:11:38.840 --> 01:11:41.160
You have seen it yourself.

01:11:41.360 --> 01:11:43.880
But you have to be really tyrannical to perfect yourself.

01:11:44.080 --> 01:11:47.720
That should be the way we should work it out

01:11:47.920 --> 01:11:50.120
towards ourselves.

01:11:50.320 --> 01:11:54.240
And towards others it should be an ideal relationship.

01:11:54.440 --> 01:11:57.240
Like now you have a brother, he is your brother

01:11:57.440 --> 01:11:58.960
- should be ideal brother.

01:11:59.200 --> 01:12:03.040
If he is your father, he should be an ideal. But such a confusion!

01:12:03.240 --> 01:12:05.440
The more enlightened, so-called, you become,

01:12:05.640 --> 01:12:07.560
the more elevated you become,

01:12:07.840 --> 01:12:10.400
the confusion is: who is your sister, who is your mother,

01:12:10.600 --> 01:12:12.960
who is your father?

01:12:13.840 --> 01:12:17.880
Then the relationship between the Sahaja yogis also becomes confused.

01:12:18.080 --> 01:12:19.880
You are Sahaja Yogis, you are all prophets,

01:12:20.080 --> 01:12:21.240
you must respect each other.

01:12:21.440 --> 01:12:24.760
You are all prophets, you speak the same language.

01:12:25.000 --> 01:12:26.560
You have to love each other.

01:12:26.760 --> 01:12:28.640
It's not rational, it has to happen to you

01:12:28.920 --> 01:12:30.840
because the relationship has to be established,

01:12:31.040 --> 01:12:34.400
that relationship, that ideal relationship.

01:12:34.600 --> 01:12:37.520
So many people now you have known that get angry with Me,

01:12:37.720 --> 01:12:40.040
"Mother, You are too patient with the Sahaja yogis."

01:12:40.240 --> 01:12:45.520
But they are My children. I have to perfect Myself,

01:12:45.760 --> 01:12:48.400
and My relationship with them should be ideal.

01:12:48.600 --> 01:12:51.480
I have to go to a great extent forgiving them

01:12:51.680 --> 01:12:54.160
so that they come up.

01:12:54.400 --> 01:12:56.880
So relationship with others should be ideal.

01:12:57.080 --> 01:12:59.840
Are you an ideal father? Are you an ideal mother?

01:13:00.040 --> 01:13:03.800
Are you an ideal sister and a brother?

01:13:04.000 --> 01:13:08.520
Are you an ideal citizen towards others?

01:13:08.720 --> 01:13:11.840
But the society has to be pragmatic.

01:13:12.200 --> 01:13:15.160
The society has to work it out pragmatically,

01:13:15.400 --> 01:13:18.520
and the pragmatic working out comes by changing.

01:13:18.720 --> 01:13:21.920
Supposing today I would say that for India

01:13:22.120 --> 01:13:24.440
we don't need vegetarianism.

01:13:24.800 --> 01:13:28.720
For England we need vegetarianism.

01:13:29.200 --> 01:13:32.680
It's all pragmatic. The society has to be pragmatic.

01:13:32.880 --> 01:13:36.160
Here, we are pragmatic about ourselves,

01:13:36.360 --> 01:13:39.680
not about the society, we are pragmatic about ourselves.

01:13:39.880 --> 01:13:42.640
Everything works out. "What's wrong?"

01:13:43.000 --> 01:13:45.480
A woman who has children will run away with another man.

01:13:45.680 --> 01:13:47.600
"What's wrong?"

01:13:47.800 --> 01:13:50.720
Or a woman who has children can sell

01:13:50.960 --> 01:13:56.240
the country for the sake of her children. "What's wrong?"

01:13:56.560 --> 01:14:00.280
So this confusion within us creates this problem,

01:14:00.480 --> 01:14:03.560
and that's how we do not know how to open out ourselves.

01:14:03.760 --> 01:14:07.520
If we could get rid of our confusions, it could be all right.

01:14:07.720 --> 01:14:09.960
It can be done through Sahaja Yoga.

01:14:10.200 --> 01:14:12.920
All these confusions have been created by half-baked people

01:14:13.120 --> 01:14:14.320
I would say.

01:14:14.520 --> 01:14:19.280
Like there's nothing wrong with the incarnations, with the prophets,

01:14:19.480 --> 01:14:23.600
nothing wrong with them, they are perfect people.

01:14:23.880 --> 01:14:26.240
What is wrong with us is our attitude.

01:14:26.600 --> 01:14:29.720
And if we can discriminately use our attitude

01:14:29.920 --> 01:14:34.120
towards ourselves, towards others and towards the society,

01:14:34.320 --> 01:14:39.440
everything will work out. It's going to be beautiful.

01:14:40.760 --> 01:14:44.800
Because of this confusion our heart is closed.

01:14:45.000 --> 01:14:48.240
We are frightened of others. What is there to be frightened?

01:14:48.520 --> 01:14:53.600
Relationship is ideal. What can we do?

01:14:54.400 --> 01:14:56.800
Your relationship as far as they are concerned,

01:14:57.000 --> 01:14:59.480
your relationship, your heart is ideal.

01:14:59.680 --> 01:15:00.960
Whatever they do is not the point.

01:15:01.200 --> 01:15:04.480
Whatever I do for them has to be ideal.

01:15:04.680 --> 01:15:08.480
I have to go on loving them.

01:15:08.680 --> 01:15:12.840
I have to go on admiring them, encouraging them, sustaining them

01:15:13.040 --> 01:15:16.800
and giving them what I have to do as My relationship has to.

01:15:17.000 --> 01:15:24.640
Say for example, a source of water that is under the Mother Earth -

01:15:25.040 --> 01:15:28.400
does it think what kind of a tree it is,

01:15:28.600 --> 01:15:30.400
what sort of things it is doing?

01:15:30.640 --> 01:15:33.800
It just gives its source, its water.

01:15:34.240 --> 01:15:38.760
In the same way, because you are the source,

01:15:39.040 --> 01:15:41.600
so the relationship has to be ideal.

01:15:41.800 --> 01:15:43.720
These confusions have worked out

01:15:43.920 --> 01:15:46.640
and rationally we have accepted all these confusions.

01:15:46.920 --> 01:15:50.200
And this has led us into this kind of a trap

01:15:50.400 --> 01:15:53.720
that our hearts are closed.

01:15:59.000 --> 01:16:01.280
All right?
